A 13-YEAR-OLD girl was taken to hospital after falling at the Time Capsule ice rink.It is believed the girl was on a school trip when the accident occurred yesterday morning. The extent of her injuries was not known.A spokesman for North Lanarkshire Leisure confirmed she was treated at the scene by trained staff and a paramedic who was in the venue at the time.He said: &quot;Our thoughts are very much with them and we wish the girl involved a speedy recovery.&quot;